photos.name: Stare - Jaguar (Pardus onca)
photos.description:
A particularly captivating shot of a mature male Jaguar through broken light from above. With the foreground taking up quite so much of the frame, the intensity of the stare is even more defined. The dark backdrop contrasts hugely with the fierce pride of the cat and his penetrating stare.

www.lightorflight.com
